canonical:
  title: 夜宿月溪
  author: 申溥
  language: lzh
  text: 移舟來泊月溪西兩岸岩回碧樹低知有隔林茅舍近半江殘月曉鷄啼
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 夜宿月溪
  author: 申溥
  language: lzh
  text: 移舟來泊月溪西。兩岸岩回碧樹低。知有隔林茅舍近。半江殘月曉鷄啼。
korean:
  title: 야숙 월계
  author: 신부
  language: kor
  text: |-
    배를 옮겨 월계 서쪽 닿았더니
    두 언덕 바위 돌고 푸른 숲이 나지막
    알겠다 수풀 넘어 띠집이 가까운 줄
    반 강 이지러진 달에 새벽 닭 울음 소리
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1460_010_0410&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: A Night's Rest at Moon Stream
  author: Shin Bo
  language: eng
  text: |-
    I moor my boat on the western shore of Moon Stream.
    Rounded rocks frame both banks, green trees bend low.
    Beyond the woods I sense it now—a thatched cottage near.
    Across the half-lit river, a rooster cries at dawn.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: Moon Stream (月溪) likely refers to a specific location known for its scenic beauty, combining the poetic imagery of moonlight and flowing water.
  - key: ''
    value: The 'half-lit river' captures the liminal moment between night and dawn, with the moon waning as daylight approaches.
